854. Titanum: Men. pretends to regard the Senex as one of the Titans warring against Apollo. Not perceiving that the combina- tion tremulum Titanum is a comic absurdity purposely introduced, most edd. follow Meursius in altering to Tithonum (the husband of Aurora, cursed with immortality without immortal youth).
